{"id": "art-2432", "label": "Art. 2432", "title": "Art. 2432", "slug": "art-2432", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1577475102\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1800\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1577475102\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 243<sup>2</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1749536316\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1799\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1749536316\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Administratorii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncare particip&#259; la fuziune sau la divizare trebuie s&#259; întocmeasc&#259;\nun raport scris, detaliat, în care s&#259; explice proiectul de fuziune sau de\ndivizare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> s&#259; precizeze fundamentul\ns&#259;u juridic <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> economic, în special cu\nprivire la rata de schimb a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>. În cazul\ndiviz&#259;rii, raportul va include, de asemenea, criteriul de repartizare a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1184319253\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1798\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1184319253\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Raportul trebuie s&#259; descrie, de asemenea, orice <span\nclass=SpellE>dificult&#259;&#355;i</span> speciale ap&#259;rute în realizarea\nevalu&#259;rii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_207395798\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1797\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_207395798\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul diviz&#259;rii, raportul administratorilor va\ninclude, dac&#259; este cazul, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> referitoare la întocmirea raportului de\nevaluare a aporturilor potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 215, pentru <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> beneficiare, <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> registrul la care acesta trebuie depus.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_444159147\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1796\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_444159147\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Administratorii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ndivizate sau, dup&#259; caz, ai fiec&#259;rei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\nimplicate în fuziune trebuie s&#259; informeze adunarea general&#259; a <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> lor, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nadministratorii celorlalte <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\nimplicate în <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span>, astfel încât <span\nclass=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span> s&#259; poat&#259; informa, la rândul lor,\nadun&#259;rile generale ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nrespective asupra oric&#259;rei modific&#259;ri <span class=SpellE>substan&#355;iale</span>\na activelor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivelor intervenite între data\nîntocmirii proiectului de divizare/fuziune <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ndata adun&#259;rilor generale care urmeaz&#259; s&#259; decid&#259; asupra\nacestui proiect. <span class=SpellE>Obliga&#355;ia</span> de informare <span\nclass=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>/<span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de administratorii celorlalte <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> implicate în <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunea</span>\nde fuziune/divizare subzist&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în cazurile\nîn care, în aplicarea art. 246<sup>1</sup>, nu este convocat&#259; adunarea\ngeneral&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>/<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1001838852\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1795\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1001838852\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Întocmirea raportului prev&#259;zut la alin. (1) <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> comunicarea <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (4) nu sunt necesare în cazul în care decid astfel <span\nclass=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span>/<span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torii</span>\naltor valori mobiliare care confer&#259; drepturi de vot la fiecare dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> participante la fuziune sau la\ndivizare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}